---
import Discord from "../components/Discord.svelte";
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";

---

<Main>
	<main class="px-5 text-center py-28 mb-5">
		<h1 class="text-gray-50 text-4xl py-1">Hi my name is Steven.</h1>
		<h2 class="text-2xl">Im a Engineer by trade and a Maker by passion.</h2>
		<div class="w-1/2 mx-auto">
			<h3 class="py-5 text-xl">Welcome to my little corner of the internet.</h3>
			<hr class="solid">
			<p class="py-2">As I return to work this is where I have decided to track my journey. I don't like social media so that method of sharing was dead in the water, and this presented a particular freedom i've been looking for when it comes to expressing myself online.</p>
			<p class="py-2">I've been doing web development since I was around 10 years of age, at that time just tinkering with html,css and a bit of php. There's always been a beautiful sense of artistry to me when it comes to designing the user expreience that helps deliver a message or product.</p>
			<p class="py-2">That's why after a bit of thought and consideration I settled on hosting my own blog.</p>
			<p class="py-2">I not only intend to track my journey back into the Information Technology field but also post about what I am currently working on and occasionally journal on new technology I find interesting.</p>
			<p class="pt-2 pb-5">I can't wait to look back one day on this page and have all the memories to enjoy. I hope you are excited to see this page evolve with me and join me in my journey.</p>
			<hr class="solid">
			<Discord />
		</div>

	</main>
</Main>